Rules.InvariantScript:
If(
    IsBlank(LadiesProductType.Selected.Colour),
    Filter(
        OurProducts,
        Gender = "Ladies"
    ),
    GroupBy(
        Filter(
            OurProducts,
            Colour = LadiesProductType.Selected.Colour
        ),
        "Colour",
        "ColourGroup"
    )
)

If(
    IsBlank(LadiesProductType.Selected.Brands),
    Filter(
        OurProducts,
        Gender = "Ladies"
    ),
    GroupBy(
        Filter(
            OurProducts,
            Brands = LadiesProductType.Selected.Brands
        ),
        "Brands",
        "BrandsGroup"
    )
)
